item.title: Asia Avelino
item.dc:creator: raratheme
item.content:encoded: Thank you very much for the prompt delivery and delicious food you delivered to us on Friday, July 28 at 3:30 p.m. Our gathering was a success due to your wonderful food.

item.title: Judy Folkmanis
item.dc:creator: raratheme
item.content:encoded: I just wanted to take a minute to tell you how WONDERFUL everything was for the party. Everything was SUPERB and delicious & every other synonym in the book. Even thought we only had about 30 people, there was enough for at least twice that number, & we are still happily munching on leftovers. The presentation was flawless and the quality was impecdable. I could go on & on, but I twould become redundant real fast. Thank you all for helping us celebrate my birthday in a first-class way. My only regret is that it took me so long to find you!

item.title: Scottie Hill
item.dc:creator: raratheme
item.content:encoded: We've always had really wonderful experiences when using Ann's for catering, but this time you really outdid yourselves! About a week ago we learned that we had 100 VIPs coming to visit our campus - yipes! Sarah as great and worked with us on short n otice to make th eevent a success. The food dropped off for us last night was wonderful, just the right amount, and made a huge impression on our guests.

item.title: Chris Schraeder
item.dc:creator: raratheme
item.content:encoded: Thank you so much for making my 50th birthday party such a wonderful success. The food was absolutely delicious, and I've passed "Ann's Catering" along to my friends sor future reference. I really enjoyed working with all of you. I'll be calling again next year to have you cater my daughter's high school graduation party.

item.title: Rachel Quilici
item.dc:creator: raratheme
item.content:encoded: Just wanted to thank you again...as usual, everything was yummy and perfect and our guests were happy guests!

item.title: Christopher Baum
item.dc:creator: raratheme
item.content:encoded:
I want to thank you all for the excellent catering this weekend - everything went beautifully and we were very pleased with both the service and the wonderful food. Our attendees unanimously enjoyed the meals, and commented on the high quality. I also wanted to mention and thank the servers at the catered event who were friendly and professional.
Again, thank you for everything. I am very pleased that we chose your services for the event!
